lucid

had a dream last night.
alone with a most beautiful
stranger
wrapped together on a bench
sitting somewhere familiar,
holding
each other,
arms stretched around her
watching the world
float softly over the moon,
intoxicated by the scent of
her hair and the soft heavens
therein,
her bare neck on my lips,
delicate intimacies.

and still, inside some
small touch of breath,
i could taste the simple unease
of longing for you.
